    "content": "When disaster strikes, you expect your insurance to cover the damage. But Chubb's adjusters work to **save the company money**, not to get you paid. Their goal? **Minimize or deny your claim.**\n\n### **The Truth About Chubb**\n\nChubb sells itself as a premium insurance provider. But when it's time to file a claim, you face delays, lowball offers, or outright denials. Their adjusters only pay for what you specifically mention, leaving out damages you may not realize are covered. The result? **You get less than you should.**\n\n### **Max Adjust Works for You, Not the Insurance Company**\n\nMax Adjust fights to **get you paid every dollar you deserve**. Unlike Chubb, we work for you—not them.\n\n-   ✅ **We secure higher payouts** - We assess all damages to ensure you claim everything.\n-   ✅ **We cover your living expenses** - If your home is unlivable, we make sure your insurance pays for temporary housing.\n-   ✅ **We recover lost income** - If the damage impacts your job or business, we fight to include lost wages and profits.\n-   ✅ **We handle negotiations** - No need to deal with Chubb's tactics. We take care of everything.\n-   ✅ **We restore your property** - We don't just file claims. We help rebuild your home.\n\n### **Get What You Deserve**\n\nChubb's goal is to pay you as little as possible. Max Adjust's goal is to **maximize your payout**. Don't let Chubb control what you get—let us fight for you.\n\n📞 **Call now for a FREE consultation. Let's get you paid!**",
